{"tid":1501082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳公安發post 表示英國駐港總領館雇員鄭文傑對嫖妓被捕事實供認不諱","createTime":"2019-08-24T08:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T11:38:16.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e6671f112f8ef162ed52a95a92f47307c2310e9","tid":1501082,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kh1ekN1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkh1ekN1.jpg&h=1a943dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【英國駐港總領館雇員鄭文傑行拘期滿，如期釋放】深圳羅湖公安24日發佈情況通報，英國駐香港總領館雇員鄭文傑因違反《治安管理處罰法》被處以行政拘留15日處罰。8月24日其行政拘留期滿，已如期釋放。行政拘留期間公安機關依法保障了鄭文傑的各項合法權益。鄭文傑對其違法事實供認不諱。"},{"pid":"f5e4ff1a0e6c0f9c1966c0d27d117513eb68476d","tid":1501082,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"認罪片呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe261bb441a5fcc8f363449fcd066b6164745121","tid":1501082,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e6671f112f8ef162ed52a95a92f47307c2310e9","tid":1501082,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kh1ekN1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkh1ekN1.jpg&h=1a943dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【英國駐港總領館雇員鄭文傑行拘期滿，如期釋放】深圳羅湖公安24日發佈情況通報，英國駐香港總領館雇員鄭文傑因違反《治安管理處罰法》被處以行政拘留15日處罰。8月24日其行政拘留期滿，已如期釋放。行政拘留期間公安機關依法保障了鄭文傑的各項合法權益。鄭文傑對其違法事實供認不諱。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"即係屈啦"},{"pid":"ad3045704b86980a47a9e1775d02018a7ab8a457","tid":1501082,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:38:19.000Z","msg":"轉BC<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=5accdf57\" data-auto-link target=\"_